wiki_section_text: 

intro: Emmett John Scanlan (born 31 January 1979) is an Irish actor from Dublin. He is best known for playing Brendan Brady in Hollyoaks. He appeared in the BBC Two drama The Fall in 2013 and 2014 and hitman movie Breakdown in which he appears alongside Craig Fairbrass, James Cosmo, Bruce Payne, Olivia Grant and Tamer Hassan. Scanlan has acted in BBC Three's In The Flesh series 2, and Guardians of the Galaxy.
